# üéÆ KITTY TERMINAL - COMPLETE HOTKEY GUIDE

## üìã CLIPBOARD OPERATIONS
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+C` | Copy to clipboard |
| `Ctrl+Shift+V` | Paste from clipboard |
| `Ctrl+Shift+S` | Paste from selection |

---

## ü™ü WINDOW/PANEL MANAGEMENT

### Creating Panels
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+Enter` | Create new window/panel |
| `Ctrl+Shift+N` | Create new OS window |
| `Ctrl+Shift+\` | **Split vertically** (side-by-side) |
| `Ctrl+Shift+-` | **Split horizontally** (stacked) |
| `Ctrl+Shift+W` | Close current panel |

### Navigating Between Panels
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+‚Üê` | Move to left panel |
| `Ctrl+Shift+‚Üí` | Move to right panel |
| `Ctrl+Shift+‚Üë` | Move to panel above |
| `Ctrl+Shift+‚Üì` | Move to panel below |

### Moving Panels Around
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+‚Üê` | Move current panel left |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+‚Üí` | Move current panel right |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+‚Üë` | Move current panel up |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+‚Üì` | Move current panel down |

### Resizing Panels
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+R` | Enter resize mode |
| `Ctrl+Shift+H` | Make panel narrower |
| `Ctrl+Shift+L` | Make panel wider |
| `Ctrl+Shift+K` | Make panel taller |
| `Ctrl+Shift+J` | Make panel shorter |

### Layout Controls
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+Z` | **Toggle zoom/focus** (full screen one panel) |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+L` | Switch to next layout style |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+P` | Return to previous layout |

**Available Layouts:**
- `splits` - Free-form split panels
- `stack` - All panels stacked (zoom mode)
- `tall` - One main panel + vertical stack
- `fat` - One main panel + horizontal stack
- `grid` - Even grid layout
- `horizontal` - All panels side-by-side
- `vertical` - All panels stacked

---

## üìë TAB MANAGEMENT

### Basic Tab Operations
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+T` | Create new tab |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Q` | Close current tab |
| `Ctrl+Shift+‚Üí` | Next tab |
| `Ctrl+Shift+‚Üê` | Previous tab |
| `Ctrl+Shift+.` | Move tab forward |
| `Ctrl+Shift+,` | Move tab backward |
| `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+T` | Rename current tab |

### Jump to Specific Tab
| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+1` | Jump to tab 1 |
| `Ctrl+2` | Jump to tab 2 |
| `Ctrl+3` | Jump to tab 3 |
| `Ctrl+4` | Jump to tab 4 |
| `Ctrl+5` | Jump to tab 5 |
| `Ctrl+6` | Jump to tab 6 |
| `Ctrl+7` | Jump to tab 7 |
| `Ctrl+8` | Jump to tab 8 |
| `Ctrl+9` | Jump to tab 9 |

