## üîó URL & TEXT HINTS

| Hotkey | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `Ctrl+Shift+E` | **Show all URLs** (click with keyboard) |
| `Ctrl+Shift+P` then `F` | Hint file paths |
| `Ctrl+Shift+P` then `H` | Hint hashes (commits, etc.) |
| `Ctrl+Shift+P` then `L` | Hint lines |
| `Ctrl+Shift+P` then `W` | Hint words |

